metrics_conclusion: In terms of chords and melody, Shadowboxer is significantly more complex than the typical song, having above average scores in Chord Complexity, Melodic Complexity, Chord-Melody Tension, Chord Progression Novelty and Chord-Bass Melody.
key_conclusion: Shadowboxer has sections analyzed in the following keys: D Dorian,  and C Major.  Click on the linked cheat sheets for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

metadata.editComments: The song is detuned on purpose, but there's no option to do that here. So I just transposed it to the nearest key.
Original song is detuned, transposed to nearest key.
